high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter behind you
Open the cupboard in front of you and grab the bucket
Turn around and walk to the fridge and open it
Put the bucket inside and close the fridge door
Open the fridge door and pick up the bucket
Walk to the microwave and place the bucket inside of it and close the door
anns.task_desc: Place a bucket into the microwave

high_descs: Turn around, go to the counter near the toaster.
Open up cabinet below the toaster and pull out the grey container.
Bring the container to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put container in, close fridge.
Open the fridge, take out the container and bring it to the microwave.
Open microwave, place container in microwave, close microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place the gray container in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to your left then move forward then left again head to the cabinet below the toaster
Open the cabinet on your right then pick up the bowl then close the cabinet
Turn to your left then head to the fridge on your left
Open the fridge put in the bowl wait for a second then get it and close the fridge
Turn left move slightly the face the microwave on your right
Put the bowl inside the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled bowl in the microwave

high_descs: Turn left and go to the sink, then turn left and go to the counter
Take out a container from the cupboard
Turn left, then left, and go to the fridge
Put the container on the top shelf in the fridge and wait a bit then take the container out of the fridge
Turn left and go towards the sink then turn right and face the microwave
Put the container in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled container into the microwave

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the sink, then hang a left and walk up to the counter.
Open the cabinet door that is second to the right of the oven and take out the glass bowl, then close the cabinet door.
Turn left and walk u to the stool, then turn left and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the bowl inside then close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the bowl, then close the fridge door.
Turn left and walk towards the sink, then turn right to face the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the chilled glass bowl inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled glass bowl in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the counter right of the stove
Pick up the clear dish from the counter
Turn and walk over to the fridge
Put the dish into the fridge and take it back out
Turn left and approach the microwave
Put the dish into the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled dish into the microwave
